{"tid":2099593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初選求求大家支持黃碧雲","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T03:47:04.000Z","uid":335967,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57fb9680eee64bd3c698322dfe083cb04841bb90","tid":2099593,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"黃碧雲咁想為大家沖，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家一定要支持佢嚟緊四年繼續喺街頭衝，唔使入議會受難。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今個禮拜六日就係初選投票日</span>， 但好似仲係冇乜人知， 國安法下再行泛民老屎忽嗰套已經唔work， <span style=\"color: red;\">大家請all in本土/素人，進行議會攬炒，踢走傳統泛民政棍。 </span><br />\n<br />\n快啲撳下低條link check下自己係邊個票站投票:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hhtN88GYnpPI6P_WRJGPD8TxEsoJFUcOAS3trzu3faQ/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hhtN88GYnpPI6P_WRJGPD8TxEsoJFUcOAS3trzu3faQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=ebb7207a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hhtN88GYnpPI6P_WRJGPD8TxEsoJFUcOAS3trzu3faQ/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4qTVym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4qTVym.jpg&h=320da228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJeUEZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJeUEZ2.jpg&h=68199461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得話埋畀身邊親朋戚友初選投票詳情！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同場加推:<br />\n(正視聽) 今次選舉目的唔係為左民主35+,係為左D